   International:
   World Wire
   ----
   Compiled by William Mathewson
</HL>
<DATE>
09/13/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A12
</SO>
<CO>
   EUROP FREST J.DHM G.BMW E.ILA AFRIC
</CO>
<IN>
MEDIA, PUBLISHING, BROADCASTING, ELECTRONIC PUBLISHING (MED)
AUTOMOBILES (AUT)
RAILROADS (RAI)
AIRLINES (AIR)
