</SO>
<CO>
   WNEWS IP
</CO>
<IN>
RAW AND FINISHED PAPER PRODUCTS (PAP)
</IN>
<LP>
   INTERNATIONAL PAPER Co. (Purchase, N.Y.) -- The paper and
forest products giant named three executives to new posts.
Newland A. Lesko, previously staff vice president and
director of quality management, was named vice president for
coated papers. Mr. Lesko is succeeded by David A. Bailey,
previously manager at the Androscoggin mill in Jay, Maine.
Paul T. Stecko, previously manufacturing manager at the
Hammerhill division, was named vice president of
manufacturing for the Hammerhill and pulp divisions.
</LP>
